==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Eighteen
<hw>Eight"een`</hw> <pr>(⟦amac⟧"t⟦emac⟧n`)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[AS.
<ets>eahtat⟦ymac⟧ne</ets>, <ets>eahtat⟦emac⟧ne</ets>. See
<er>Eight</er>, and <er>Ten</er>, and cf. <er>Eighty</er>.]</ety>
<def>Eight and ten; <as>as, <ex>eighteen</ex> pounds</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Eighteen</ent>⟦br⟧

==== ENTRY 2 ====
HEADWORD: Eighteen
<hw>Eight"een`</hw>, <pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>The number greater
by a unit than seventeen; eighteen units or objects.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>A symbol denoting eighteen units, as 18 or
xviii.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Eighteenmo</ent>⟦br⟧
